
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5001/api/v1
@authToken = <PASTE_YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE>
@studentToken = <PASTE_YOUR_STUDENT_TOKEN_HERE>

### Get All Questions (Public/Student View - correct_answer hidden)
GET {{baseUrl}}/questions

### Get Questions by Filter (Grade 12, Public/Student View)
GET {{baseUrl}}/questions?grade=12

### Get Questions with Pagination (Page 2, Limit 5)
GET {{baseUrl}}/questions?page=2&limit=5

### Get Questions with Sorting (Sort by difficulty ascending)
GET {{baseUrl}}/questions?sort=difficulty

### Get Questions with Sorting (Sort by grade descending and createdAt ascending)
GET {{baseUrl}}/questions?sort=-grade,createdAt

### Get Questions with Advanced Filtering (Difficulty greater than or equal to 3)
GET {{baseUrl}}/questions?difficulty[gte]=3

### Get Questions with Multiple Filters (Grade 10, Difficulty 2, Type SELECT)
GET {{baseUrl}}/questions?grade=10&difficulty=2&type=SELECT

### Get Questions for Admin/Teacher (correct_answer visible if token is ADMIN/TEACHER)
GET {{baseUrl}}/questions
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Get Specific Question by ID (Public/Student View - correct_answer hidden)
GET {{baseUrl}}/questions/65a2a2e2b2e2e2e2e2e2e2e2

### Get Specific Question by ID (Admin/Teacher View - correct_answer visible)
GET {{baseUrl}}/questions/65a2a2e2b2e2e2e2e2e2e2e2
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Create Question (Requires ADMIN/TEACHER Token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/questions
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "grade": 12,
  "chapter_id": "GIAI_TICH_12_C1",
  "difficulty": 2,
  "type": "SELECT",
  "content": "Tính đạo hàm của hàm số $y = x^2$.",
  "options": [
    {"id": "A", "text": "$y' = x$"},
    {"id": "B", "text": "$y' = 2x$"},
    {"id": "C", "text": "$y' = 2$"},
    {"id": "D", "text": "$y' = 0$"}
  ],
  "correct_answer": ["B"],
  "explanation": "Công thức đạo hàm của $x^n$ là $nx^{n-1}$."
}

### Update Question (Requires ADMIN/TEACHER Token)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/questions/65a2a2e2b2e2e2e2e2e2e2e2
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "difficulty": 3,
  "content": "Tính đạo hàm của hàm số $y = x^3$.
}

### Delete Question (Requires ADMIN/TEACHER Token)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/questions/65a2a2e2b2e2e2e2e2e2e2e2
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
